::Shadow Wing::

She didn't like feeing this way.  She knew that revenge was a predacon 
emotion and not one for a Maximal.  She tried to put it out of her mind, but 
she still thought about striking back at them for all the damage that they 
caused.  She thought about all the good bots that they killed. This has to 
stop somewhere, she thought.  She went to the entrance of the new base.  She 
saw Lunarpine walking out.
"Where are you going?"
